Detailed Description

This class represents a vcard and it was used in VCardEntryHandler.

The following example demonstrates how to use the VCardImporter class.

 gaia::vcard::VCardEntry* entry = new gaia::vcard::VCardEntry();
 gaia::base::String displayName = entry->getDisplayName();
 gaia::base::String birthday = entry->getBirthday();
 gaia::base::StringArray websiteArray = entry->getWebsite();

 if (entry != NULL) {
     delete entry;
     entry = NULL;
 }

Constructs the array of insert operation.

The returned array is filled with new insert operations. When operationList argument is not NULL, this method appends those new operations into the object instead of creating a new Array.
